Date: Mon, 26 May 2025 18:06:38 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 04/11] QSDK:DP:wifi: Add PPE-DS Support for QCN6432 radio

Add support registering and managing the PPEDS ring interrupts

Patch-dependency:
        325-QSDK-DP-wifi-Add-support-for-PPE-DS-Direct-switch-fe.patch
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Nithyanantham Paramasivam <nithp@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
