 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/ahb.c    | 133 ++++++++++++++++++++++-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/ppe.h    |   1 +
 3 files changed, 134 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

